Discworld player help
smithy

.SH Name
.SI 5
smithy - a place where you can fix your belongings.
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
If you are competent enough in smithing to have the 'fix' command,
you can make use of the facilities in this room to repair your weapons
and armours. 
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> fix cost sword
To fix a long sword it would probably cost you about A$2.77.
> fix sword
You fix up a long sword.
It costs you A$3.15.

.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
